<h1>How can we make your experience more personal?</h1>
<p class="lead">When you decide to sign up for a Culture Companion account, one of the things that we recommend you do first is to take a short survey. The survey will ask you a few easy questions, such as how old you are and what you're interests are. This information will be used not only to help us make your experience better in the future, but also to curate your <i>Recommended</i> section - when you're ready to move onto something else, we can provide some handy suggestions on what we think you might like.</p>

