<h1>How do you earn points?</h1>
<p class="lead">Every time you tag onto a display article using NFC, QR codes or its unique ID, we'll give you some points! Your points will be kept on your account, and you'll be able to track your progress through our exhibits on your <i>Profile</i> page. Tag all displays in an exhibit to get 100% completion, then prove you're an expert on the topic by trying our exhibit quizzes to earn even more points!</p>

<h1>What do the points do?</h1>
<p class="lead">We understand that kids can sometimes need a bit of persuation when it comes to learning, and with Culture Companion we award points for doing just that! Completing quizzes in each exhibit will unlock bonus digital content such as wallpapers and printable crafts. More points will score you small discounts in the gift store and for some exhibits, there may even be small goodie bags waiting in the gift shop for those who've done well.</p>

